  $General information$
    Every menu consists of options specific to this menu and 3 other options: `Back`, `Help`, `Exit`.

    #Back#
      Moves to a previous menu.

    #Help#
      Provides a description and a guide to all the options contained in the menu.

    #Exit#
      Exits the application without need of backtracking to the main menu.

